    {
      "id": "detailed_1_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is in absolute mint condition and looks as if it just rolled off the showroom floor. The exterior paint is flawless with a deep, mirror-like shine and zero scratches, chips, or dents. Inside, the cabin is pristine, with the leather upholstery and trim showing no signs of wear or aging. Mechanically, the car is perfect, having been meticulously maintained with a full service history and all original components in peak working order. This is a rare find for a collector or an enthusiast who demands the highest possible quality.",
